title: Bright 2 bedroom in NE Minneapolis
posting_body: ['Bright two bedroom plus sun porch.', ' Upper unit on duplex.', ' Great location in NE Minneapolis.', ' Great shared back yard space/patio.', '•\tHardwood floors throughout and tons of natural light.', '•\t2 bedrooms', '•\tNo pets', '•\tNot section 8 approved', '•\tIn unit washer and dryer', '•\tClosets and storage.', '•\tApartment has dedicated water heater, no need to race the neighbors for a hot shower :)', '•\tWalk to restaurants, shops, and brew houses (Grumpy’s, Hai Hai, Stanleys, Jax, Market Bar-B-Que, Carma Coffee, Fulton Brewing, Mojo Coffee, Psycho Suzi’s, Tony Jaro’s, Better Danger’s, Shaw’s, Mayslack’s, Anchor Fish and Chips, Dangerous Man Brewing, Young Joni, and many more)', '•\tOne off street parking spot is included in the rent.', '•\t2 blocks to busline', '•\tNo smoking in building', 'Available Sept 1st or Oct 1st.', ' Can be earlier, let us know what you’re looking for.', '$1375/month plus electric', '$1375 sec.', 'deposit', '1 year lease and then month to month', 'following the 1 year lease.', 'This property is not section 8 approved and does not allow pets.', 'Please mention 5th St when responding to this add.']
